789
00:23:09,840 --> 00:23:19,760
 Pogodit će to svakoga i imat ćete izbor kad se suočiti sa bolestom i patnjom.

790
00:23:19,760 --> 00:23:21,940
 I to katekizem priznaje.

791
00:23:21,940 --> 00:23:29,700
 Piše ovdje da je to najteže pitanje i moguće da neki očajavaju u tom trenutku.

792
00:23:29,760 --> 00:23:32,420
 I ja sam to vidio. Ja sam to vidio.

793
00:23:32,420 --> 00:23:39,400
 Ja sam čak to vidio kod nekih svečenika koji na kraju života tako teško trpe da padaju u očaj.

794
00:23:39,400 --> 00:23:49,760
 Ali s druge strane, katekizem također govori da bolest može čovjeka tako uzdići

795
00:23:49,760 --> 00:23:54,860
 da on postane bolji i svetiji i da zapravo doživi Boga u tome.

796
00:23:55,800 --> 00:24:01,160
 Dakle, uvijek znajte kad vi doživljavate bol, trpljenje i patnju da imate jedan izbor.

797
00:24:01,160 --> 00:24:08,200
 Šta ćete vi sa svojom slobodom učiniti sa patnjom i boli sa kojim vi suočavate?

798
00:24:08,200 --> 00:24:13,540
 I ovo je vrlo konkretno jer ja znam ovdje među ovom publikom ima ljudi konkretno koji trpe.

799
00:24:13,540 --> 00:24:16,440
 I to fizički i također duševno.

800
00:24:17,480 --> 00:24:21,380
 Što činite s tim? Šta to čini od vas?

801
00:24:21,380 --> 00:24:26,660
 Jel vi postajete gora osoba ili svetija osoba?

802
00:24:26,660 --> 00:24:31,460
 Ja ću vam samo reći da ili će biti jedno ili drugo.

803
00:24:31,460 --> 00:24:34,220
 Zato je ovo jako važno pitanje.

804
00:24:34,220 --> 00:24:36,720
 Naše društvo nema odgovor na ovo.

805
00:24:36,720 --> 00:24:39,060
 Naše društvo nema odgovor na ovo.

806
00:24:39,880 --> 00:24:42,360
 Naše društvo ima zapravo dva odgovora.

807
00:24:42,360 --> 00:24:47,480
 Ukloni bol pod svakom sjenom ili ubija.

808
00:24:47,480 --> 00:24:49,040
 Eutanazija.

809
00:24:49,040 --> 00:24:54,140
 Ubija ili ukloni bol do te mjere da on ne zna čak za sebe.

810
00:24:54,140 --> 00:24:59,280
 Međutim, ja to ne mogu prihvatiti.

811
00:24:59,280 --> 00:25:04,820
 Ne samo ja, nego i naša crkva izaziva nas.

812
00:25:04,820 --> 00:25:07,760
 Djeca crkve, mi smo svi djeca crkve.

813
00:25:08,260 --> 00:25:13,180
 Crkva nas izaziva da ne idemo u ove dvije krajnosti.

814
00:25:13,180 --> 00:25:17,140
 Da ne idemo po svakom cijenom ukloni svaku bol.

815
00:25:17,140 --> 00:25:21,380
 Da bježimo od toga i s problemi smo činiti u sve samo da se ukloni.

816
00:25:21,380 --> 00:25:23,720
 I druga krajnost, naravno, je ubiga.

817
00:25:23,720 --> 00:25:28,360
 Što braćo i sestre, nažalost, ušli smo u tu fazu povijesti

818
00:25:28,360 --> 00:25:31,140
 gdje eutanazija nam kuca na velika vrata.

819
00:25:31,140 --> 00:25:31,840
 Nažalost.

820
00:25:31,840 --> 00:25:34,460
 I neke evropske zemlje su već to odobrile.

821
00:25:34,460 --> 00:25:37,860
 Čini mi se, susedi naši slovenci su odobrili.

822
00:25:38,960 --> 00:25:41,920
 Dakle, bolest može čovjeka dovesti do tjeskobe,

823
00:25:41,920 --> 00:25:47,140
 do zatvaranja, ponakad čak do očaje i pobune proti Boga.

824
00:25:47,140 --> 00:25:47,700
 Čak to.

825
00:25:48,380 --> 00:25:52,880
 Ili bolest čovjeka može izazvat da Boga traži i da mu se vrati.

826
00:25:52,880 --> 00:25:55,960
 Ja ne znam za drugi izbor. Samo su ta dva izbora.

827
00:25:55,960 --> 00:26:01,880
 Koliko je meni bolno bilo, kao župnik ovdje tri godine,

828
00:26:01,880 --> 00:26:06,680
 upisivajući sprovode kad neko umre.

829
00:26:07,540 --> 00:26:11,160
 I pitanje koje ja pitam, jedna rubrika postoji tamo,

830
00:26:11,160 --> 00:26:15,660
 pita se od čega je umro i je li primio posne sakrmeta,

831
00:26:15,660 --> 00:26:16,640
 oboleško pomazanje.

832
00:26:16,640 --> 00:26:19,300
 Braćo i sestre, tako je tužno čut.

833
00:26:19,300 --> 00:26:23,240
 Ja ne znam statistiku, ali to je mizerna brojka.

834
00:26:23,240 --> 00:26:25,520
 Dakle, 95% ne prima.

835
00:26:26,360 --> 00:26:29,560
 Ja uvijek pitan, pa dobro, zašto nas niste zvali?

836
00:26:29,560 --> 00:26:31,240
 Znate što mi svi odgovaraju?

837
00:26:31,240 --> 00:26:32,660
 Nismo znali da ću umriti.

838
00:26:32,660 --> 00:26:34,980
 A vi na tamo 28. godište rekao, jel?

839
00:26:34,980 --> 00:26:38,480
 Nisi znao da ću umrijeti.

840
00:26:38,480 --> 00:26:44,280
 I on dan, pazite sad ovo, izrade smrtovnicu,

841
00:26:44,280 --> 00:26:47,780
 čak uplate u večernjaku Slobodna Dalmacija,

842
00:26:47,780 --> 00:26:50,700
 jutarnji, ono na zadnje par stranica one oglase

843
00:26:50,700 --> 00:26:55,940
 i kaže, u dubokoj tuzi javljamo iznenada je umro.

844
00:26:56,360 --> 00:26:58,800
 I tamo vidiš 95 godina, jel?

845
00:26:58,800 --> 00:27:02,400
 Ja rekao, gospođo draga, bolje da upišete u novima

846
00:27:02,400 --> 00:27:06,480
 iznenada se oženio za sina ili iznenada diplomiro.

847
00:27:06,480 --> 00:27:08,680
 To je meni puno veće.

848
00:27:08,680 --> 00:27:11,540
 Nije smrti iznenađenje.

849
00:27:11,540 --> 00:27:14,600
 To je jedino što ja znam da će se dogoditi.

850
00:27:14,600 --> 00:27:19,000
 To je jedine što ja znam da će se meni dogoditi.

851
00:27:19,000 --> 00:27:20,360
 Ja ću umrijeti.

852
00:27:20,360 --> 00:27:21,800
 Umrijet ću.

853
00:27:21,800 --> 00:27:26,100
 I kako se suočavamo s time?

854
00:27:26,360 --> 00:27:29,120
 Kako se s time suočavamo?

855
00:27:29,120 --> 00:27:36,320
 Jer vi znate da je to najvažniji trenutak tvog života.

856
00:27:36,320 --> 00:27:37,200
 Znate zašto?

857
00:27:37,200 --> 00:27:41,480
 Jer u tom trenutku odlučuješ cijelu vječnost.

858
00:27:41,480 --> 00:27:42,700
 Sami ste vi to?

859
00:27:42,700 --> 00:27:49,120
 Da u tom trenutku ti možeš zapravo odlučit se.

860
00:27:49,120 --> 00:27:51,300
 To je na radnik 11. ure.

861
00:27:51,300 --> 00:27:57,720
 Cijelu svoja, cijela tvoja vječnost visi o tom trenutku.

862
00:27:57,720 --> 00:28:02,980
 Zato molimo u zdravo Marije sada i na času smrti.

863
00:28:02,980 --> 00:28:03,300
 Amen.

864
00:28:03,300 --> 00:28:05,900
 Zapravo dva su najvažnija trenutaka života.

865
00:28:05,900 --> 00:28:06,400
 Znate koja?

866
00:28:06,400 --> 00:28:08,040
 Sada i smrt.

867
00:28:08,040 --> 00:28:11,500
 Budući da sada se odmah pretvaraju u nova sad jer vrijeme ide.

868
00:28:11,500 --> 00:28:12,760
 Svaki trenutak je važan.

869
00:28:12,760 --> 00:28:16,080
 To je dosta zgodno rečeno u zdravo Marije.

870
00:28:16,080 --> 00:28:17,560
 Sada i na času smrti.

871
00:28:17,560 --> 00:28:21,100
 Ja želim u času smrti biti spreman.

872
00:28:21,100 --> 00:28:24,420
 Ja želim ne bježati.

873
00:28:24,420 --> 00:28:26,920
 Ja želim se s tim suočiti i biti spreman.

874
00:28:26,920 --> 00:28:34,460
 Zato crkva, majka crkva, koja želi biti svojom djecom u svakoj fazi života.

875
00:28:34,460 --> 00:28:37,780
 Zato od rođenja, majka crkva želi tu pa te krstimo.

876
00:28:37,780 --> 00:28:41,540
 U odrastanju mi želimo tu biti, zato te hranimo Ehoristijom.

877
00:28:41,900 --> 00:28:44,100
 Zato te saljamo u krizmi, da te osnažimo.

878
00:28:44,100 --> 00:28:45,260
 Zato te ženimo.

879
00:28:45,260 --> 00:28:49,800
 Dakle, ko svaki roditelj, ti želiš biti s tvojim djetetom u svakom trenutku.

880
00:28:49,800 --> 00:28:53,360
 I u trenutku kad su zločestni moraš ih disciplinirati.

881
00:28:53,360 --> 00:28:54,360
 Zato imamo ispovjed.

882
00:28:54,360 --> 00:28:59,980
 I tako majka crkva želi biti sa svojom djecom kad ona umre.

883
00:28:59,980 --> 00:29:01,200
 Kad ona umire.

884
00:29:01,200 --> 00:29:03,740
 I zato imamo ovaj sakravenat.

885
00:29:03,740 --> 00:29:09,560
 Kao što sam već spomenio, to je Isus Krist ustanovio.

886
00:29:10,560 --> 00:29:15,320
 I što se tiče naziva, ono se prije zvalo posljedna pomast,

887
00:29:15,320 --> 00:29:18,860
 ali u novije vrijeme, Bogu hvala, ono se zove bolestiško pomazanje.

888
00:29:18,860 --> 00:29:20,520
 I Bogu hvala na tome.

889
00:29:20,520 --> 00:29:21,140
 Zašto?

890
00:29:21,140 --> 00:29:23,460
 Jer ima ljudi u našim selima.

891
00:29:23,460 --> 00:29:29,300
 Ne znam, evo, to je iz razloga zašto prosječan Hrvat neće zvati svećenika.

892
00:29:29,300 --> 00:29:32,240
 Zato što kad vide svećenika, gotovo je smrt.

893
00:29:32,240 --> 00:29:34,720
 To je to, on nosi smrt.

894
00:29:34,720 --> 00:29:36,620
 Pa je, pa ja.

895
00:29:36,620 --> 00:29:38,940
 I zato taj izraz mi nije dobar.

896
00:29:38,940 --> 00:29:39,980
 Posljedna pomast.

897
00:29:39,980 --> 00:29:41,480
 Ne, bolestiško pomazanje.

898
00:29:41,480 --> 00:29:42,760
 Si bolestan?

899
00:29:42,760 --> 00:29:43,240
 Jesi.

900
00:29:43,240 --> 00:29:44,980
 Evo, ja sam tu za tebe.

901
00:29:44,980 --> 00:29:51,240
 Zato neki kažu, ja mislim kad već požuti, kad mu ust ne drte,

902
00:29:51,240 --> 00:29:53,460
 evo sad ćemo svećenika zvati.

903
00:29:53,880 --> 00:29:56,760
 Krivo, krivo, krivo.

904
00:29:56,760 --> 00:29:58,020
 Okej, nemojte to.

905
00:29:58,020 --> 00:30:01,760
 Pogotovo vi koji imate nekoga doma ili koji ste bolestni.

906
00:30:01,760 --> 00:30:05,040
 Što mene tiče, svi koji preko 65 godina su kandidati.

907
00:30:05,040 --> 00:30:08,380
 Kakvi? Svi preko 60 su kandidati.

908
00:30:08,380 --> 00:30:09,860
 Okej.

909
00:30:09,860 --> 00:30:15,060
 E, slušajte ovo.

910
00:30:15,060 --> 00:30:16,100
 Pazite sad ovo.

911
00:30:16,100 --> 00:30:19,680
 Tko smije primati bolestiško pomazanje?

912
00:30:20,900 --> 00:30:25,840
 Znate, crkva je vrlo, kad piše dokumenta, ona je sjednostavno vrlo općenita.

913
00:30:25,840 --> 00:30:29,420
 Ona sve kaže, ali i neke ljudima to ide na živce.

914
00:30:29,420 --> 00:30:33,700
 A to je što točno ne opisuje detalje.

915
00:30:33,700 --> 00:30:37,960
 Naprimjer, ja ne znam, jel vi očekujete dva tkana, neka mora biti treći stadiju, rak.

916
00:30:37,960 --> 00:30:41,880
 Ne znam šta očekujete, ali ovo su kriteriji.

917
00:30:41,880 --> 00:30:42,520
 Kaže ovako.

918
00:30:42,520 --> 00:30:48,260
 Zbog bolesti ili starosti koji se nalazi na početku smrtne pogeblje.

919
00:30:49,880 --> 00:30:52,840
 I kao što vidite, to se može tumačiti kako hoćeš, jel?

920
00:30:52,840 --> 00:30:58,760
 Ali meni je drago što naša crkva ne ide u takve detalje, da je apsolutno sve definirano.

921
00:30:58,760 --> 00:31:00,380
 Ovdje se daje jedna sloboda.

922
00:31:00,380 --> 00:31:06,440
 Kaže, ovaj se sakrament može ponoviti ako bolestnik po primljenoj pomasti prizdravi,

923
00:31:06,440 --> 00:31:08,340
 a onda nastupi druga teška bolest.

924
00:31:08,340 --> 00:31:10,320
 Dakle, sakrament se može ponoviti.

925
00:31:11,220 --> 00:31:17,680
 Također ovdje kaže, u tijeku iste bolici sakrament se može ponoviti ako nastupi pogoršenje.

926
00:31:17,680 --> 00:31:24,120
 Čak ovdje kaže, prije kiruškog zahvata. Čak to piše u dokumentu.

927
00:31:24,120 --> 00:31:26,360
 Ja mislim da je to jedan napredak.

928
00:31:27,360 --> 00:31:31,940
 I Bogu fala, ljudi kažu, velčastinu operaciju i tako dalje.

929
00:31:31,940 --> 00:31:32,940
 I to je okej.

930
00:31:32,940 --> 00:31:40,100
 I kaže, isto vrijedi i za starije osobe kojih nemoć biva sve veća.

931
00:31:40,100 --> 00:31:42,420
 Sad, ko ima uši, neka čuje.

932
00:31:42,420 --> 00:31:50,000
 Kada sam ja kao svećenik odbio bolestčko pomazanje,

933
00:31:50,000 --> 00:31:52,660
 najgore mi je kad mi dođe trudnica.

934
00:31:52,660 --> 00:31:56,120
 I kaže, draga moja, ko ti je rekao da je trudnoća bolest?

935
00:31:56,380 --> 00:32:00,260
 To ne. Neko dođe, ima migrenu, glavobolju.

936
00:32:00,260 --> 00:32:04,240
 Ona je, malo pitaš, nije spavao sinoć jer je bančio van

937
00:32:04,240 --> 00:32:06,360
 i sad ga glava boli, traži blešku pomazanje.

938
00:32:06,360 --> 00:32:07,980
 Ne, draga, aj ti spava i pi vodu.

939
00:32:07,980 --> 00:32:15,540
 Mislim, obično ja sam, vidite, upoznam svećenike koji dijele šakom i kapom.

940
00:32:15,540 --> 00:32:17,000
 Ja sam protiv toga.

941
00:32:17,000 --> 00:32:21,120
 Ja sam malo, malo tu konzervativni.

942
00:32:21,120 --> 00:32:24,840
 Ja mislim da to bi trebao biti osoba koja je starija,

943
00:32:25,020 --> 00:32:28,140
 koja već malo pomalo se gasi, slabiji u tijelu,

944
00:32:28,140 --> 00:32:31,440
 koji ide na kiruški zakvat i koji ima ozbilnu dijagnozu.

945
00:32:31,440 --> 00:32:34,500
 Oni su za bolestičko pomazanje.

946
00:32:36,360 --> 00:32:39,860
 Još jedna sitnica, samo svećenici i biskupi smije.

947
00:32:39,860 --> 00:32:42,860
 Dakle, džako ne lajkne, samo svećenik i biskupi.

948
00:32:42,860 --> 00:32:45,220
 I to dolazimo od Jakovljave poznanice.

949
00:32:45,220 --> 00:32:48,060
 I također Marko 6 gdje Isus ne šalja svakoga,

950
00:32:48,060 --> 00:32:49,540
 njegove apostole.

951
00:32:49,540 --> 00:32:52,460
 Dakle, na temelju toga crkva smatra,

952
00:32:53,780 --> 00:32:56,060
 i vjeruje i drži od početka,

953
00:32:56,060 --> 00:33:00,420
 da samo svećenik i da samo biskup može to dijeliti.

954
00:33:00,420 --> 00:33:01,500
 Onaj koji ima sveti red.

955
00:33:01,500 --> 00:33:03,780
 Ok, kako to slavlje izgleda?

956
00:33:03,780 --> 00:33:07,540
 Evo, ja sam čak donio obrednik bleškog pomazanja

957
00:33:07,540 --> 00:33:11,160
 i ja ću to malo s vama proć.

958
00:33:11,160 --> 00:33:15,680
 I zanimljivo, počinje sa škropljenjem vode.

959
00:33:15,680 --> 00:33:17,780
 Jako zanimljivo.

960
00:33:17,780 --> 00:33:18,780
 Znate zašto?

961
00:33:18,780 --> 00:33:22,460
 Zato što prvi put kad si ti poškropljen vodom

962
00:33:22,460 --> 00:33:24,200
 je bilo krštenje.

963
00:33:24,200 --> 00:33:27,700
 A na dan krštenja ti si umro samom sebi.

964
00:33:27,700 --> 00:33:32,500
 Nasupra što ljudi misle,

965
00:33:32,500 --> 00:33:35,080
 krštenje je sakrmenat križa.

966
00:33:35,080 --> 00:33:36,880
 Mnogi ljudi to ne povezuju, ali jest.

967
00:33:36,880 --> 00:33:39,580
 Isus se kaže da se ima krsti s svojim krstom

968
00:33:39,580 --> 00:33:41,040
 i omizi na smrt svoju.

969
00:33:41,040 --> 00:33:45,940
 I zato ono uranjanje u vodu,

970
00:33:45,940 --> 00:33:47,740
 iako mi škropimo, mi poljevamo,

971
00:33:47,740 --> 00:33:50,400
 ali može se uranjati i izlazi novi čovjek.

972
00:33:50,400 --> 00:33:52,740
 I tako mi je lijepo

973
00:33:52,740 --> 00:33:55,700
 da ovaj sakrmenat počinje

974
00:33:55,700 --> 00:33:58,040
 na podsjetnik tvog krštenja.

975
00:33:58,040 --> 00:34:01,000
 Kako počinje obred sprovod,

976
00:34:01,000 --> 00:34:02,680
 to nije sakrmenat, obred sprovod,

977
00:34:02,680 --> 00:34:04,560
 škropimo lije si tijelo.

978
00:34:04,560 --> 00:34:06,840
 Predivno nešto.

979
00:34:06,880 --> 00:34:11,440
 To znači uska povezanost između krštenja

980
00:34:11,440 --> 00:34:12,600
 i bleško pomazanje.

981
00:34:12,600 --> 00:34:13,700
 Mi prvo te škropimo.

982
00:34:13,700 --> 00:34:14,760
 To je prvo.

983
00:34:16,120 --> 00:34:19,820
 Nakon toga svećenik ima poticajnu riječ.

984
00:34:19,820 --> 00:34:22,860
 Čak ima ovdje jedan predložak,

985
00:34:22,860 --> 00:34:24,440
 kao jedan uvodni nagovor.

986
00:34:24,440 --> 00:34:27,540
 I obično to su riječi utjehe,

987
00:34:27,540 --> 00:34:30,300
 to su riječi poticanje na vjeru,

988
00:34:30,300 --> 00:34:32,380
 na nadu, na ufanje i tako dalje.

989
00:34:32,380 --> 00:34:33,580
 Spomenje se ovo Jakova

990
00:34:33,580 --> 00:34:34,940
 i spomenje se da je Isus živ.

991
00:34:35,060 --> 00:34:36,800
 Dakle, pobuđujem vjeru.

992
00:34:36,800 --> 00:34:40,700
 I svjestan sam da mnogi moji brača svećenici

993
00:34:40,700 --> 00:34:42,060
 malo to ofrljera.

994
00:34:42,060 --> 00:34:43,480
 Ne svi, ali neki da.

995
00:34:43,480 --> 00:34:45,800
 Ali ovo bi trebalo biti slavljeno.

996
00:34:45,800 --> 00:34:48,060
 I predlaže se da bude zajedno u obitelji.

997
00:34:48,060 --> 00:34:49,900
 U zajedništu.

998
00:34:49,900 --> 00:34:52,020
 Predlaže se čak da bude pod misom,

999
00:34:52,020 --> 00:34:52,820
 ako je moguće.

1000
00:34:52,820 --> 00:34:56,300
 Predlaže se da se čovjek ispovidi prije.

1001
00:34:56,780 --> 00:34:58,620
 U slučaju da se neko nije ispovidio,

1002
00:34:58,620 --> 00:35:00,560
 pokajanje za grijehe.

1003
00:35:00,560 --> 00:35:03,300
 Nakon škropljenja vode,

1004
00:35:03,300 --> 00:35:04,040
 nakon podstav vjere,

1005
00:35:04,040 --> 00:35:07,020
 on nam svećenik poziva na kajanje za grijehe.

1006
00:35:07,020 --> 00:35:12,500
 Jer svaka bolest u širem smislu vječi

1007
00:35:12,500 --> 00:35:14,820
 dolazi od prvog pada čovjeka.

1008
00:35:14,820 --> 00:35:16,900
 I zato mi se odričimo grijeha.

1009
00:35:16,900 --> 00:35:18,040
 Mi se kajemo za to.

1010
00:35:18,040 --> 00:35:21,820
 Nakon toga slijedi navještaj riječ Božije.

1011
00:35:21,820 --> 00:35:26,020
 Dakle, crkva ima prekrasne neke predložke

1012
00:35:26,020 --> 00:35:27,380
 tu iz evanđelje.

1013
00:35:27,380 --> 00:35:29,640
 I onda bi strbalo slijedi podstavne riječi.

1014
00:35:29,640 --> 00:35:30,900
 Opet malo kratka propovjed.

1015
00:35:30,900 --> 00:35:32,460
 Navještaj evanđelje toj osobi.

1016
00:35:32,460 --> 00:35:35,020
 I onda kreće molitva vjernika.

1017
00:35:35,020 --> 00:35:36,480
 Moli se za tog bolesnika.

1018
00:35:36,480 --> 00:35:38,280
 Moli se za oni koji ga dvore.

1019
00:35:38,280 --> 00:35:39,440
 Moli se za sve bolesnike.

1020
00:35:39,440 --> 00:35:39,940
 I tako dakle.

1021
00:35:39,940 --> 00:35:41,380
 Gdje mi molimo zajedno.

1022
00:35:41,380 --> 00:35:45,240
 Nakon toga, jako lijepo,

1023
00:35:45,240 --> 00:35:46,240
 jako lijepo,

1024
00:35:46,240 --> 00:35:49,580
 zazivam molitvu presvetog trojstva.

1025
00:35:49,580 --> 00:35:51,220
 Otac, sin i dug sveti.

1026
00:35:51,220 --> 00:35:54,840
 Predivne molitve gdje još jednom zazivamo trojstvo.

1027
00:35:55,260 --> 00:35:59,220
 I onda na jednom trenutku svećinik polaže ruke.

1028
00:35:59,220 --> 00:36:00,640
 Baš utišini.

1029
00:36:00,640 --> 00:36:01,680
 Utišini.

1030
00:36:01,680 --> 00:36:04,480
 Od svih polaganja ruke,

1031
00:36:04,480 --> 00:36:05,840
 u svim sakramentima,

1032
00:36:05,840 --> 00:36:09,800
 vjerujte mi da mi je ovo najdublje.

1033
00:36:09,800 --> 00:36:11,200
 Baš utišini.

1034
00:36:11,200 --> 00:36:12,580
 Samo utišini.

1035
00:36:13,100 --> 00:36:14,060
 Polaže se ruke.

1036
00:36:14,060 --> 00:36:16,280
 Jer svećiničke ruke su pomazane.

1037
00:36:16,280 --> 00:36:21,040
 I svećinik kratko se zaustavi iznad glave i polaže ruke nad njim.

1038
00:36:21,040 --> 00:36:22,240
 I naravno,

1039
00:36:22,240 --> 00:36:22,820
 nakon toga,

1040
00:36:22,820 --> 00:36:25,320
 vjernik ispruži svoje ruke.

1041
00:36:25,320 --> 00:36:27,220
 I ja ću pročitati formulu.

1042
00:36:27,620 --> 00:36:28,400
 svećinik moli,

1043
00:36:28,400 --> 00:36:30,440
 po ovome svetom pomazanju

1044
00:36:30,440 --> 00:36:32,320
 i po svome preblago milosređu,

1045
00:36:32,320 --> 00:36:34,680
 nekada gospodin milošću duha svetoga pomogne.

1046
00:36:34,680 --> 00:36:38,020
 I tada napravim križić sa posvećenim uljem na čelo.

1047
00:36:38,020 --> 00:36:38,960
 Nakon toga,

1048
00:36:38,960 --> 00:36:41,220
 nekada te oslobođena od grijeha spasi

1049
00:36:41,220 --> 00:36:42,700
 i milostivo podigne.

1050
00:36:43,080 --> 00:36:44,480
 I onda pomazujem ruke,

1051
00:36:44,480 --> 00:36:45,080
 dlanove.

1052
00:36:45,080 --> 00:36:50,020
 I što se tiče tog ulja,

1053
00:36:50,020 --> 00:36:52,400
 to nije bilo koje ulje.

1054
00:36:52,400 --> 00:36:54,160
 To je masino ulje

1055
00:36:54,160 --> 00:36:56,140
 koje je posvetio nadbiskup.

1056
00:36:56,140 --> 00:36:58,740
 Samo da vam malo približim nešto o tom ulju.

1057
00:36:58,740 --> 00:37:01,140
 To nije ulje koje sam ja zvao

1058
00:37:01,140 --> 00:37:02,620
 nekog moj prijeta na braću.

1059
00:37:02,620 --> 00:37:04,280
 Ej, imaš ulje, aj pošaljim na bus.

1060
00:37:04,280 --> 00:37:06,160
 Ne, ne.

1061
00:37:06,160 --> 00:37:08,560
 Znate ko je to ulje?

1062
00:37:08,560 --> 00:37:11,380
 Vrijedi ovo spominjan.

1063
00:37:12,120 --> 00:37:13,620
 Ja nisam nikad radio masano ulje.

1064
00:37:13,620 --> 00:37:15,700
 Ali navodno,

1065
00:37:15,700 --> 00:37:17,860
 kad se radi to masano ulje,

1066
00:37:17,860 --> 00:37:20,240
 ti stari kameni mlinovi,

1067
00:37:20,240 --> 00:37:21,820
 sad ne znam kako oni to rade danas,

1068
00:37:21,820 --> 00:37:23,020
 ali navodno onaj,

1069
00:37:23,020 --> 00:37:24,600
 znate ono masne,

1070
00:37:24,600 --> 00:37:25,980
 kad onaj kamen,

1071
00:37:25,980 --> 00:37:27,460
 ona preša,

1072
00:37:27,460 --> 00:37:28,920
 zgniječi,

1073
00:37:28,920 --> 00:37:32,020
 ono prvo ulje što iskoči,

1074
00:37:32,020 --> 00:37:32,540
 ono pl.

1075
00:37:32,540 --> 00:37:34,920
 Ej, to ulje se koristi.

1076
00:37:34,920 --> 00:37:36,480
 Jer navodno,

1077
00:37:36,480 --> 00:37:38,220
 oni više puta to ulje vraćaju,

1078
00:37:38,220 --> 00:37:39,720
 pa masne, pa opet,

1079
00:37:39,720 --> 00:37:41,120
 pa imaš drugu rundu, treću rundu.

1080
00:37:41,180 --> 00:37:42,880
 Ne, ne, ne, prva runda ide sveći,

1081
00:37:42,880 --> 00:37:44,800
 prva runda ide za sakrmet.

1082
00:37:44,800 --> 00:37:46,340
 Zamijeste vi to,

1083
00:37:46,340 --> 00:37:48,240
 ono prvo što izađe.

1084
00:37:48,240 --> 00:37:51,440
 To se pohrani

1085
00:37:51,440 --> 00:37:54,140
 i na veliki četvrtak.

1086
00:37:54,140 --> 00:37:56,600
 To je jedina misa u godinu

1087
00:37:56,600 --> 00:37:57,540
 koja ima svoju temu.

1088
00:37:57,540 --> 00:37:59,460
 Dakle, svake nedelje imamo mise,

1089
00:37:59,460 --> 00:38:00,840
 ali jedina misa

1090
00:38:00,840 --> 00:38:01,940
 koja ima svoju temu,

1091
00:38:01,940 --> 00:38:03,580
 to je misa posveta ulja.

1092
00:38:03,660 --> 00:38:04,200
 tako se zove.

1093
00:38:04,200 --> 00:38:06,000
 To je veliki četvrtak ujtru,

1094
00:38:06,000 --> 00:38:07,460
 uvijek u katedrali,

1095
00:38:07,460 --> 00:38:08,160
 ne bilo gdje,

1096
00:38:08,160 --> 00:38:09,160
 nego u katedrali.

1097
00:38:09,160 --> 00:38:11,020
 Ta misa je toliko svećana

1098
00:38:11,020 --> 00:38:12,320
 da su sve druge mise

1099
00:38:12,320 --> 00:38:14,520
 dilijem nadbiskupije zabranjene.

1100
00:38:14,520 --> 00:38:16,180
 Zato veliki četvrtak

1101
00:38:16,180 --> 00:38:17,000
 nema jutarnje mise.

1102
00:38:18,000 --> 00:38:19,300
 Svake godine ljudi kucu

1103
00:38:19,300 --> 00:38:20,360
 E, otvaraj.

1104
00:38:20,360 --> 00:38:22,680
 Nema mise, zašto?

1105
00:38:22,680 --> 00:38:23,900
 Velika četvrtak,

1106
00:38:23,900 --> 00:38:24,860
 pa zato sam tu.

1107
00:38:24,860 --> 00:38:26,460
 Pa, onda ja moram njemu

1108
00:38:26,460 --> 00:38:27,700
 cijelu teologiju objasniti.

1109
00:38:27,700 --> 00:38:30,220
 Nema mise, veliki četvrtak,

1110
00:38:30,220 --> 00:38:30,660
 nigdje,

1111
00:38:30,660 --> 00:38:32,660
 samo u katedrali.

1112
00:38:32,660 --> 00:38:35,680
 Svaki svećenik je dužan doć.

1113
00:38:35,680 --> 00:38:37,400
 Čak ako ne dođeš,

1114
00:38:37,400 --> 00:38:38,580
 moraš se ispričati,

1115
00:38:38,580 --> 00:38:39,560
 moraš imati razlog.

1116
00:38:39,560 --> 00:38:40,880
 Mislim, ovo je ozbiljna stvar.

1117
00:38:40,880 --> 00:38:42,660
 I na toj misi

1118
00:38:42,660 --> 00:38:44,400
 nadbiskup,

1119
00:38:44,400 --> 00:38:45,620
 ne neki svećenik,

1120
00:38:45,620 --> 00:38:46,660
 neko nadbiskup

1121
00:38:46,660 --> 00:38:48,640
 posvećuje to ulje.

1122
00:38:48,640 --> 00:38:51,140
 Čime će se pomazivati

1123
00:38:51,140 --> 00:38:52,500
 sve bolestnike tijekom godine.

1124
00:38:52,500 --> 00:38:53,620
 I mi župnici,

1125
00:38:53,620 --> 00:38:54,000
 odnosno,

1126
00:38:54,000 --> 00:38:54,380
 kog godine,

1127
00:38:54,380 --> 00:38:55,440
 dad sam ja bio župnik,

1128
00:38:55,440 --> 00:38:56,900
 dođeš i dobiješ

1129
00:38:56,900 --> 00:38:58,160
 odmah nakon mise,

1130
00:38:58,160 --> 00:38:59,680
 dobiješ svoju ampolicu

1131
00:38:59,680 --> 00:39:02,180
 ulje za cijelu godinu.

1132
00:39:02,180 --> 00:39:04,520
 Bolesničko i krizmaničko.

1133
00:39:04,520 --> 00:39:05,460
 Ok?

1134
00:39:05,460 --> 00:39:07,240
 Evo, braćo i seste,

1135
00:39:07,240 --> 00:39:08,140
 to je to ulje.

1136
00:39:08,140 --> 00:39:10,340
 To je to posvećeno ulje.

1137
00:39:10,340 --> 00:39:12,460
 Koje sve je to ulje.

1138
00:39:12,460 --> 00:39:14,660
 S time mi pomazujemo

1139
00:39:14,660 --> 00:39:15,980
 naše vjernike.

1140
00:39:16,460 --> 00:39:18,600
 Ovo nisam mislio govoriti,

1141
00:39:18,600 --> 00:39:20,760
 ali smatrao sam važnim.

1142
00:39:20,760 --> 00:39:21,520
 Nakon toga,

1143
00:39:21,520 --> 00:39:22,700
 molimo zajedno.

1144
00:39:22,700 --> 00:39:23,680
 I tako,

1145
00:39:23,680 --> 00:39:25,420
 sakrmenat je dovršen.

1146
00:39:25,420 --> 00:39:26,040
 Ok.

1147
00:39:26,040 --> 00:39:28,620
 Znate šta je meni puno važnije?

1148
00:39:28,620 --> 00:39:32,020
 Učin si ovog sakrmenata.

1149
00:39:32,020 --> 00:39:33,700
 Učin si.

1150
00:39:35,300 --> 00:39:36,380
 ima nekoliko učinaka.

1151
00:39:36,380 --> 00:39:39,260
 Ja moram priznat kao svećenik,

1152
00:39:39,260 --> 00:39:40,600
 danas sam ja ostao paf.

1153
00:39:40,600 --> 00:39:41,020
 Evo ga.

1154
00:39:41,020 --> 00:39:43,020
 Ja, Bož mi,

1155
00:39:43,020 --> 00:39:44,260
 nisam znao neke stvari.

1156
00:39:44,260 --> 00:39:45,240
 Evo, ja sam danas

1157
00:39:45,240 --> 00:39:47,380
 ovo iznova naučio.

1158
00:39:47,380 --> 00:39:49,300
 Ne iznova prvi put.

1159
00:39:50,440 --> 00:39:52,920
 jesam ja prespavao to na KBF-u,

1160
00:39:52,920 --> 00:39:53,360
 ne znam,

1161
00:39:53,360 --> 00:39:53,760
 jesam,

1162
00:39:53,760 --> 00:39:56,740
 ali,

1163
00:39:56,740 --> 00:40:00,220
 evo, jedva čekam da podijelim sakrmenat.

1164
00:40:00,220 --> 00:40:01,160
 Evo, sljedeći puta.

1165
00:40:01,160 --> 00:40:02,720
 Ne želim nikome bolest,

1166
00:40:02,720 --> 00:40:02,920
 ali.

1167
00:40:05,580 --> 00:40:06,560
 Ok, prvo.

1168
00:40:06,560 --> 00:40:08,160
 Ovo su učinci.

1169
00:40:08,160 --> 00:40:10,140
 Kaže,

1170
00:40:10,140 --> 00:40:12,520
 osnovna milost ovog sakrmenata

1171
00:40:12,520 --> 00:40:13,700
 je milost potpore,

1172
00:40:13,700 --> 00:40:15,320
 mira i ohrabrenja.

1173
00:40:15,320 --> 00:40:17,560
 Za nadvladanje tegoba,

1174
00:40:17,560 --> 00:40:18,080
 vlasti,

1175
00:40:18,080 --> 00:40:19,040
 teškoj bolesti

1176
00:40:19,040 --> 00:40:20,620
 ili staračkoj nemoći.

1177
00:40:20,620 --> 00:40:23,920
 Danas mi pada naprijed

1178
00:40:23,920 --> 00:40:25,040
 ovoj prvo svjedočanstvo.

1179
00:40:25,040 --> 00:40:28,420
 Ja sam jednom podijelio

1180
00:40:28,420 --> 00:40:29,500
 beličko poznajem mom tati.

1181
00:40:29,500 --> 00:40:31,620
 Ok, to je bilo slučajno.

1182
00:40:31,620 --> 00:40:33,300
 U smislu,

1183
00:40:33,300 --> 00:40:35,300
 imao sam pučke misije

1184
00:40:35,300 --> 00:40:35,960
 u Kanadi,

1185
00:40:35,960 --> 00:40:36,640
 u Misisagi,

1186
00:40:36,640 --> 00:40:37,540
 župa Misisaga.

1187
00:40:37,540 --> 00:40:38,520
 I naravno,

1188
00:40:38,520 --> 00:40:40,220
 moji roditelji su dolazi svaku večer.

1189
00:40:40,220 --> 00:40:41,520
 I župnik je tako zamislio.

1190
00:40:41,520 --> 00:40:42,860
 Sedan dana sam bio za redu.

1191
00:40:42,860 --> 00:40:45,400
 Jednu večer župnik je zamislio

1192
00:40:45,400 --> 00:40:47,200
 pokorničko i bleško pomezanje.

1193
00:40:47,200 --> 00:40:49,500
 I mi smo imali taj uvodni obred

1194
00:40:49,500 --> 00:40:50,160
 i tako dalje.

1195
00:40:50,160 --> 00:40:51,000
 I najavljeno,

1196
00:40:51,000 --> 00:40:52,320
 bolesnici i starsi došli.

1197
00:40:52,320 --> 00:40:54,260
 Ja uopće nisam razmišljao.

1198
00:40:54,260 --> 00:40:55,340
 Ja gledam u redu,

1199
00:40:55,340 --> 00:40:56,160
 moj tata stoji.

1200
00:40:56,160 --> 00:40:58,980
 Bilo mi je malo neugodno.

1201
00:40:58,980 --> 00:40:59,920
 Ja sam htio da moj tata...

1202
00:40:59,920 --> 00:41:00,220
 Mislim,

1203
00:41:00,600 --> 00:41:02,660
 jednom mi je brat došao za ispred

1204
00:41:02,660 --> 00:41:03,340
 i ja sam ga potiruo.

1205
00:41:03,340 --> 00:41:05,940
 Mislim,

1206
00:41:05,940 --> 00:41:08,380
 prvo nisam znao kako ću reagirati.

1207
00:41:08,380 --> 00:41:09,500
 Ja nisam znao

1208
00:41:09,500 --> 00:41:11,540
 oče to mene ganuti.

1209
00:41:11,540 --> 00:41:13,800
 Nisam baš u tom trenutku

1210
00:41:13,800 --> 00:41:15,500
 htio neke emocije pokazati.

1211
00:41:15,500 --> 00:41:16,140
 Mislim,

1212
00:41:16,140 --> 00:41:18,220
 stoji predamnom čovjek

1213
00:41:18,220 --> 00:41:19,060
 koji je moj tata,

1214
00:41:19,060 --> 00:41:22,620
 čije tijelo slabi,

1215
00:41:22,620 --> 00:41:25,240
 koji je krh i slab,

1216
00:41:25,340 --> 00:41:26,240
 a on je za mene

1217
00:41:26,240 --> 00:41:27,660
 simbol autoriteta

1218
00:41:27,660 --> 00:41:28,940
 i muževnost

1219
00:41:28,940 --> 00:41:29,520
 i muškost

1220
00:41:29,520 --> 00:41:30,060
 i sve to

1221
00:41:30,060 --> 00:41:32,260
 i on stoji predamnom.

1222
00:41:32,260 --> 00:41:35,060
 Ja sam ga pomozao

1223
00:41:35,060 --> 00:41:36,700
 i ništa.

1224
00:41:36,700 --> 00:41:37,540
 Idemo dalje.

1225
00:41:37,540 --> 00:41:39,540
 I sutradan,

1226
00:41:39,540 --> 00:41:41,280
 kad smo bili sami,

1227
00:41:41,280 --> 00:41:42,860
 moj tata me povuče za rukav

1228
00:41:42,860 --> 00:41:44,020
 i to je prvi put

1229
00:41:44,020 --> 00:41:44,420
 da vam prima

1230
00:41:44,420 --> 00:41:45,340
 bleško pomozanje.

1231
00:41:45,340 --> 00:41:47,360
 Znate šta mi je tata rekao?

1232
00:41:47,360 --> 00:41:48,000
 Kaže,

1233
00:41:48,000 --> 00:41:48,380
 sine,

1234
00:41:48,380 --> 00:41:51,600
 nikad u životu

1235
00:41:51,600 --> 00:41:53,300
 nisam takav mir doživio.

1236
00:41:54,680 --> 00:41:55,780
 I to mi je danas palo napnije

1237
00:41:55,780 --> 00:41:57,720
 i to je prvi učinak ovog svega.

1238
00:41:57,720 --> 00:41:59,100
 Ja nisam znao da je to učinak.

1239
00:41:59,100 --> 00:42:00,400
 Ja danas to prvi put učitam.

1240
00:42:00,400 --> 00:42:02,480
 Ponoviću.

1241
00:42:02,480 --> 00:42:04,120
 Milost,

1242
00:42:04,120 --> 00:42:04,880
 potpore,

1243
00:42:04,880 --> 00:42:06,440
 mir i ohrabrenje.

1244
00:42:06,440 --> 00:42:07,840
 Ok?

1245
00:42:07,840 --> 00:42:10,380
 I možda nećeš ozdraviti.

1246
00:42:10,380 --> 00:42:12,520
 Možda ćeš ti ostati

1247
00:42:12,520 --> 00:42:13,420
 u svoj bolesti.

1248
00:42:13,420 --> 00:42:15,900
 Ali Krist Isus

1249
00:42:15,900 --> 00:42:17,380
 želi ti dat mir

1250
00:42:17,380 --> 00:42:18,860
 tada

1251
00:42:18,860 --> 00:42:20,860
 i ohrabrenje

1252
00:42:20,860 --> 00:42:21,680
 i potporu

1253
00:42:21,680 --> 00:42:23,380
 da ti to nosiš.

1254
00:42:23,380 --> 00:42:23,840
 Ok?

1255
00:42:24,020 --> 00:42:26,200
 I zato je crkva stavila

1256
00:42:26,200 --> 00:42:28,020
 ovo kao prvi učinak sakramenta.

1257
00:42:28,020 --> 00:42:29,420
 I velim,

1258
00:42:29,420 --> 00:42:30,340
 to mi je danas palo napnije

1259
00:42:30,340 --> 00:42:31,240
 kad mi je tata rekao

1260
00:42:31,240 --> 00:42:33,100
 i moj tata je

1261
00:42:33,100 --> 00:42:33,600
 Bogu falo

1262
00:42:33,600 --> 00:42:34,600
 82 godine.

1263
00:42:34,600 --> 00:42:35,080
 Slabi,

1264
00:42:35,080 --> 00:42:35,760
 totalno.

1265
00:42:35,760 --> 00:42:37,100
 Ali

1266
00:42:37,100 --> 00:42:38,740
 gospodin želi tebi mir

1267
00:42:38,740 --> 00:42:39,920
 u tom trenutku.

1268
00:42:39,920 --> 00:42:41,200
 I ovaj sakrament donesi mir.

1269
00:42:41,200 --> 00:42:42,340
 Broj dva

1270
00:42:42,340 --> 00:42:44,740
 povezano.

1271
00:42:44,740 --> 00:42:45,360
 Obnavlja

1272
00:42:45,360 --> 00:42:46,000
 pouzdanje

1273
00:42:46,000 --> 00:42:46,740
 i vjeru u Boga.

1274
00:42:48,680 --> 00:42:50,000
 Znate kad sam ja ovo vidio?

1275
00:42:50,000 --> 00:42:51,180
 Kad sam bio šest dana

1276
00:42:51,180 --> 00:42:51,960
 Fraj Mihaljević

1277
00:42:51,960 --> 00:42:52,780
 za vrijeme COVID-a.

1278
00:42:52,780 --> 00:42:53,380
 Mislim,

1279
00:42:53,380 --> 00:42:55,100
 ja tada

1280
00:42:55,100 --> 00:42:56,260
 nisam htio tamo biti,

1281
00:42:56,260 --> 00:42:57,240
 nisam trebao tamo biti.

1282
00:42:57,240 --> 00:42:58,080
 Ja sam uvjeren

1283
00:42:58,080 --> 00:42:59,540
 da ja nisam trebao tamo biti.

1284
00:42:59,540 --> 00:43:00,380
 Mene ništa nije bolo.

1285
00:43:00,380 --> 00:43:01,180
 Ja došao malo,

1286
00:43:01,180 --> 00:43:02,080
 neka pozitiva,

1287
00:43:02,080 --> 00:43:03,160
 COVID, šta ja znam.

1288
00:43:03,560 --> 00:43:05,220
 I doktor nekako me prepozvalo.

1289
00:43:05,220 --> 00:43:05,400
 Sveđu,

1290
00:43:05,400 --> 00:43:06,280
 ajde, ostani te,

1291
00:43:06,280 --> 00:43:06,660
 ajde, ostani te.

1292
00:43:06,660 --> 00:43:07,400
 Pa neću ostati.

1293
00:43:07,400 --> 00:43:08,400
 Ajde, ostani, molim te.

1294
00:43:08,400 --> 00:43:09,280
 Ostani, molim te.

1295
00:43:09,280 --> 00:43:10,440
 Jarko, šta je ovo?

1296
00:43:10,440 --> 00:43:12,540
 Ja rekao,

1297
00:43:12,540 --> 00:43:13,400
 kaže, ajde,

1298
00:43:13,400 --> 00:43:14,420
 imamo slobodnu sobu,

1299
00:43:14,420 --> 00:43:14,960
 tamo ostane.

1300
00:43:14,960 --> 00:43:15,680
 Ajde, ajde,

1301
00:43:15,680 --> 00:43:16,760
 ostaću šest dana,

1302
00:43:16,760 --> 00:43:17,300
 ja ostalo,

1303
00:43:17,300 --> 00:43:18,260
 Bože, sad ću.

1304
00:43:18,260 --> 00:43:21,260
 Sutradan ja ga pitao,

1305
00:43:21,260 --> 00:43:22,120
 ja mogu ja izaću?

1306
00:43:22,120 --> 00:43:23,080
 Ne, ne, ne, ne, ne.

1307
00:43:23,080 --> 00:43:24,280
 Započeli smo terapiju,

1308
00:43:24,280 --> 00:43:24,600
 peše.

1309
00:43:24,600 --> 00:43:24,940
 I jako,

1310
00:43:24,940 --> 00:43:25,780
 ojme meni.

1311
00:43:27,220 --> 00:43:27,820
 I gledajte ovo,

1312
00:43:27,820 --> 00:43:30,900
 malo sam bio ljud,

1313
00:43:30,900 --> 00:43:33,080
 jer ja nisam trebao tamo biti.

1314
00:43:33,080 --> 00:43:36,640
 Ja apsolutno nisam trebao tamo biti.

1315
00:43:36,640 --> 00:43:38,960
 Ali gospodin me tamo postavio.

1316
00:43:38,960 --> 00:43:40,740
 Ja kužim,

1317
00:43:40,740 --> 00:43:41,520
 starci tamo,

1318
00:43:41,520 --> 00:43:42,620
 neki se guše i tako,

1319
00:43:42,620 --> 00:43:43,340
 ja zovem doma,

1320
00:43:43,340 --> 00:43:44,420
 doneste mi ulje,

1321
00:43:44,420 --> 00:43:47,320
 eukoristiju i štolu i obrnika.

1322
00:43:47,320 --> 00:43:50,500
 I gospodin se poslužio sa mnom,

1323
00:43:50,500 --> 00:43:52,700
 što se ja obilizio sve sobe.

1324
00:43:52,700 --> 00:43:54,320
 Ljudi moji,

1325
00:43:54,320 --> 00:43:55,580
 ja vam mogu reći,

1326
00:43:55,580 --> 00:43:56,760
 mojim očima sam vidio

1327
00:43:56,760 --> 00:43:59,340
 kako se obnavlja

1328
00:43:59,340 --> 00:44:00,560
 pouzdanje vjera u Boga.

1329
00:44:00,560 --> 00:44:03,400
 Kako su ljudi

1330
00:44:03,400 --> 00:44:06,560
 koji su bili usamljeni,

1331
00:44:06,560 --> 00:44:09,600
 koji nisu bili sa svojim ljubljenima,

1332
00:44:09,600 --> 00:44:11,640
 nisu mogli ući

1333
00:44:11,640 --> 00:44:13,120
 u bolnici.

1334
00:44:13,120 --> 00:44:14,360
 Znate kako je to teško.

1335
00:44:14,360 --> 00:44:16,400
 Vjerujte mi da je to teže

1336
00:44:16,400 --> 00:44:18,460
 od fizičke bolesti.

1337
00:44:18,460 --> 00:44:20,700
 Jer naj,

1338
00:44:20,700 --> 00:44:23,300
 u bolesti nije samo u onoj tableti

1339
00:44:23,300 --> 00:44:24,620
 ili inekciji ili ne znam što već,

1340
00:44:24,620 --> 00:44:26,300
 nego je ona ljubav koja te zakruže

1341
00:44:26,300 --> 00:44:28,880
 i ako ne može muž, žena, mama, tata,

1342
00:44:28,880 --> 00:44:31,040
 biti ili sin ili kći ili unuk,

1343
00:44:31,040 --> 00:44:31,540
 ne znam što već,

1344
00:44:31,540 --> 00:44:32,360
 Isus je tu.

1345
00:44:32,360 --> 00:44:35,140
 Ok, Isus je tu.

1346
00:44:35,140 --> 00:44:37,720
 I zato sam ja vidio ove dvije stvari.

1347
00:44:37,720 --> 00:44:39,920
 Ova dva učinka sam uživo gledao.

1348
00:44:39,920 --> 00:44:42,740
 Dakle, potpora, miri, ohrabrenje

1349
00:44:42,740 --> 00:44:44,720
 i pouznanje vjera u Boga.

1350
00:44:44,720 --> 00:44:47,320
 Treći učinak.

1351
00:44:47,320 --> 00:44:50,960
 Jača protiv napasti zloga.

1352
00:44:50,960 --> 00:44:52,900
 Ljudi, ako vi mislite,

1353
00:44:52,900 --> 00:44:54,860
 ako vi mislite da džava,

1354
00:44:54,860 --> 00:44:56,820
 ok, džava te napisuje kad si mlad,

1355
00:44:56,820 --> 00:44:57,820
 aj, griješi, bludno,

1356
00:44:57,820 --> 00:44:59,000
 kradi ovo, ono,

1357
00:44:59,000 --> 00:45:00,400
 on vidi, ne prolazi,

1358
00:45:00,400 --> 00:45:02,600
 ušao u brak, aj, varaj ženu,

1359
00:45:02,600 --> 00:45:03,560
 varaj muža, ajde,

1360
00:45:03,560 --> 00:45:04,500
 on je izdržao

1361
00:45:04,500 --> 00:45:07,140
 i na kraju života staraci džavao će reći,

1362
00:45:07,140 --> 00:45:07,420
 šta misli?

1363
00:45:07,420 --> 00:45:08,500
 Ili svi misli da će džavao reći,

1364
00:45:08,500 --> 00:45:09,740
 ali dobro, aj, idem,

1365
00:45:09,740 --> 00:45:11,040
 idem se baci na nekog drugog.

1366
00:45:11,040 --> 00:45:11,800
 Ma kakvi.

1367
00:45:11,800 --> 00:45:14,080
 Ljudi moji,

1368
00:45:14,080 --> 00:45:15,820
 ne želim niko uplošiti.

1369
00:45:15,820 --> 00:45:20,240
 Ja mislim da prava bitka tek počinje.

1370
00:45:20,240 --> 00:45:23,500
 Ali ja to ozbiljno govorim.

1371
00:45:23,500 --> 00:45:26,320
 Kažu svjedoci

1372
00:45:26,320 --> 00:45:28,380
 da majka Terezija,

1373
00:45:28,380 --> 00:45:29,020
 kad je umirala,

1374
00:45:29,020 --> 00:45:32,060
 da su to takve muke

1375
00:45:32,060 --> 00:45:33,260
 i napasti bili.

1376
00:45:33,260 --> 00:45:36,520
 Zamisli ti koja bi to pobjeda bila Sotoni,

1377
00:45:36,520 --> 00:45:38,380
 da je ono svetu dušu,

1378
00:45:38,380 --> 00:45:40,900
 da u zadnjem času njeznog života

1379
00:45:40,900 --> 00:45:42,600
 pada u očaj i proklinje.

1380
00:45:42,600 --> 00:45:43,960
 Zamest vi to.

1381
00:45:43,960 --> 00:45:47,120
 Kažu da je čak biskup došao,

1382
00:45:47,120 --> 00:45:48,640
 ja ne znam je to istina,

1383
00:45:48,640 --> 00:45:49,400
 navodno,

1384
00:45:49,400 --> 00:45:50,680
 ja sam negdje čitao to,

1385
00:45:50,680 --> 00:45:52,000
 da je čak biskup došao,

1386
00:45:52,000 --> 00:45:52,840
 molite eksorcizan.

1387
00:45:52,840 --> 00:45:55,400
 To su takve demonske napasti

1388
00:45:55,400 --> 00:45:55,920
 bili na nju.

1389
00:45:55,920 --> 00:45:57,500
 Bogu falu,

1390
00:45:57,500 --> 00:45:58,120
 ona izdržava.

1391
00:45:58,120 --> 00:46:00,380
 Šta mi se kroz naše bolnice

1392
00:46:00,380 --> 00:46:01,520
 da zloduh ne prolazi

1393
00:46:01,520 --> 00:46:03,340
 i ubacuje očaj.

1394
00:46:03,340 --> 00:46:04,620
 Svi su te zaboravili.

1395
00:46:04,620 --> 00:46:06,600
 Niko ne zna za te.

1396
00:46:06,600 --> 00:46:07,840
 Jedva čeka da umreš.

1397
00:46:07,840 --> 00:46:11,060
 Vidiš kako život nema smisla.

1398
00:46:11,060 --> 00:46:12,260
 Sam si.

1399
00:46:12,260 --> 00:46:14,040
 Šta mi ste,

1400
00:46:14,040 --> 00:46:15,420
 ljudi ne prolaze takve stvari.

1401
00:46:15,420 --> 00:46:18,420
 I zamisli cijeli život radiš,

1402
00:46:18,420 --> 00:46:19,940
 kreposno živiš

1403
00:46:19,940 --> 00:46:21,260
 i zadnji čas.

1404
00:46:21,260 --> 00:46:24,480
 Zloduh uspije nekoga dobiti.

1405
00:46:24,480 --> 00:46:25,840
 Mestri, to su strašne stvari.

1406
00:46:25,840 --> 00:46:29,420
 Zato ovaj sakarmenac se daje

1407
00:46:29,420 --> 00:46:31,620
 protiv jača,

1408
00:46:31,620 --> 00:46:33,480
 protiv napasti, zloga.

1409
00:46:33,480 --> 00:46:36,280
 Jer on će najviše napadat tada.

1410
00:46:36,280 --> 00:46:38,660
 Najviše će tad napadat.

1411
00:46:38,660 --> 00:46:42,540
 Zato što njega samo zanima tvoja duša.

1412
00:46:42,540 --> 00:46:44,440
 Da ti izgubiš svoju dušu.

1413
00:46:44,440 --> 00:46:47,200
 I kad će to raditi nego tada.

1414
00:46:47,200 --> 00:46:48,780
 Kada? Kad si najslabi.

1415
00:46:48,780 --> 00:46:49,400
 Kad si krk.

1416
00:46:49,560 --> 00:46:50,300
 Kad si bolestan.

1417
00:46:50,300 --> 00:46:51,220
 Kad si možda napušten.

1418
00:46:51,220 --> 00:46:52,480
 Kad imaš fizičku bol.

1419
00:46:52,480 --> 00:46:54,120
 I možda mlađi nemaju vremena.

1420
00:46:54,120 --> 00:46:54,920
 Ljudi, pogledajte.

1421
00:46:54,920 --> 00:46:56,440
 Ja to vidim mojim očima.

1422
00:46:56,440 --> 00:46:57,760
 Mladi, odoše mladi.

1423
00:46:57,760 --> 00:46:59,260
 Unuci, sinovi, kći.

1424
00:46:59,260 --> 00:47:01,500
 Roditelji su bolestni, stari.

1425
00:47:01,500 --> 00:47:02,660
 Svi zaboravljaju.

1426
00:47:02,660 --> 00:47:03,780
 Ljudi moji,

1427
00:47:03,780 --> 00:47:04,980
 znaš koji su to napasti?

1428
00:47:04,980 --> 00:47:08,280
 Zato ovaj sakarmenac

1429
00:47:08,280 --> 00:47:10,860
 upravo jača protiv te zadnje borbe.

1430
00:47:10,860 --> 00:47:13,440
 Zato se u našoj crkvi govori

1431
00:47:13,440 --> 00:47:15,180
 o takozvanoj napast

1432
00:47:15,180 --> 00:47:16,700
 posljednjeg časa.

1433
00:47:16,700 --> 00:47:18,100
 I posljedna kušnja.

1434
00:47:18,480 --> 00:47:20,740
 A to je onaj zadnji udarac.

1435
00:47:20,740 --> 00:47:21,700
 E sad ću ga dobiti.

1436
00:47:21,700 --> 00:47:23,680
 Sad ću ga dobiti da se odrekne vjere.

1437
00:47:23,680 --> 00:47:24,680
 Da proklinje Boga.

1438
00:47:24,680 --> 00:47:27,920
 I zato u tom trenutku

1439
00:47:27,920 --> 00:47:29,740
 kako je to dar Boga

1440
00:47:29,740 --> 00:47:31,000
 da dođe svečenik

1441
00:47:31,000 --> 00:47:32,860
 i bleško pomazanje donijeti.

1442
00:47:35,540 --> 00:47:37,480
 Naravno još jedan učinak

1443
00:47:37,480 --> 00:47:38,820
 ozdravljenje duše i tijela.

1444
00:47:38,820 --> 00:47:42,560
 i oproštenje grijeha.

1445
00:47:42,560 --> 00:47:44,260
 Oproštenje grijeha.

1446
00:47:44,260 --> 00:47:47,160
 Na ubleško pomazanje,

1447
00:47:47,160 --> 00:47:47,760
 na neki uz,

1448
00:47:47,760 --> 00:47:49,040
 kajanje i tako dalje

1449
00:47:49,040 --> 00:47:51,200
 može se dobiti i oproštenje grijeha.

1450
00:47:51,200 --> 00:47:54,500
 Još jedan učinak.

1451
00:47:54,500 --> 00:47:58,020
 Sjedinjenje s mukom Kristovom.

1452
00:48:00,020 --> 00:48:02,640
 učinjenje s otkupiteljskom Kristovom mukom.

1453
00:48:02,640 --> 00:48:04,180
 Sad ću ja reći nešto

1454
00:48:04,180 --> 00:48:06,120
 vrlo, vrlo kontroverzno.

1455
00:48:06,120 --> 00:48:07,580
 Ok?

1456
00:48:07,580 --> 00:48:09,220
 Ljudi,

1457
00:48:09,220 --> 00:48:11,020
 nemojte dopustiti

1458
00:48:11,020 --> 00:48:13,620
 da netko od vas

1459
00:48:13,620 --> 00:48:16,340
 oduzme iskustvo smrti.

1460
00:48:16,340 --> 00:48:17,600
 Hm.

1461
00:48:17,600 --> 00:48:19,200
 Šta to znači?

1462
00:48:19,200 --> 00:48:20,740
 Svi ćemo umrijeti.

1463
00:48:20,740 --> 00:48:24,000
 Ali se to iskustvo može oduzeti od tebe.

1464
00:48:24,000 --> 00:48:24,680
 Na koji način?

1465
00:48:24,680 --> 00:48:26,120
 Šta društvo radi?

1466
00:48:26,120 --> 00:48:27,720
 Eutanaz, već sam svoj.

1467
00:48:27,720 --> 00:48:29,260
 Totalno drogiranje.

1468
00:48:30,020 --> 00:48:31,800
 ili eutanazija.

1469
00:48:31,800 --> 00:48:35,160
 Ok, ovo, ovdje sam na vrlo tanak led

1470
00:48:35,160 --> 00:48:37,900
 jer je tako teško gledat nekoga koji trpi.

1471
00:48:37,900 --> 00:48:40,500
 Međutim,

1472
00:48:40,500 --> 00:48:43,100
 to je jedno iskustvo

1473
00:48:43,100 --> 00:48:44,740
 koje je naš gospodin prošao.

1474
00:48:44,740 --> 00:48:46,580
 Ja nisam sadista,

1475
00:48:46,580 --> 00:48:47,480
 niti mazohista

1476
00:48:47,480 --> 00:48:48,700
 da tražimo trpljenje,

1477
00:48:48,700 --> 00:48:51,640
 ali ja vidim jednu vrijednost.

1478
00:48:51,640 --> 00:48:52,700
 Mi kršćani

1479
00:48:52,700 --> 00:48:54,560
 možemo osmisliti,

1480
00:48:54,560 --> 00:48:55,100
 ne mi,

1481
00:48:55,100 --> 00:48:56,880
 nego Isus je za nas osmislio

1482
00:48:56,880 --> 00:48:59,200
 da ta muka i patnja i bol

1483
00:48:59,200 --> 00:49:00,140
 čak postane

1484
00:49:00,140 --> 00:49:01,440
 odkupiteljska

1485
00:49:01,440 --> 00:49:02,200
 za tebe

1486
00:49:02,200 --> 00:49:03,240
 i čak za druge.

1487
00:49:03,240 --> 00:49:07,220
 Ja neću

1488
00:49:07,220 --> 00:49:08,400
 dalje ovdje tumačiti.

1489
00:49:08,400 --> 00:49:08,940
 Jesam li ja

1490
00:49:08,940 --> 00:49:09,620
 protiv

1491
00:49:09,620 --> 00:49:11,040
 tablete za bolo?

1492
00:49:11,040 --> 00:49:11,600
 Nisam,

1493
00:49:11,600 --> 00:49:12,840
 ali mislim

1494
00:49:12,840 --> 00:49:14,000
 da je zdravo

1495
00:49:14,000 --> 00:49:15,200
 u jednoj mjeri

1496
00:49:15,200 --> 00:49:16,420
 doživiti,

1497
00:49:16,420 --> 00:49:18,260
 čovjek može i poginiti,

1498
00:49:18,260 --> 00:49:18,560
 ne zna što,

1499
00:49:18,560 --> 00:49:19,780
 doživiti svoj smrt.

1500
00:49:19,780 --> 00:49:21,100
 Pa to je najvažniji trenutak

1501
00:49:21,100 --> 00:49:21,500
 tvojih života.

1502
00:49:21,500 --> 00:49:22,280
 Znate šta bi ja volio?

1503
00:49:22,280 --> 00:49:23,340
 Biti pri svijesti.

1504
00:49:23,340 --> 00:49:25,680
